DESCRIPTION:Come explore Bradford Woods during our Open Gate Day on Friday
 \, May 9\, from 10 a.m. to 2 p.m.! Bring your friends and enjoy a day of 
 hiking and discovery. Admission is just $10 per carload.\nGuests will als
 o have the opportunity to purchase limited tickets for select activities 
 on a first-come\, first-served basis\, including archery ($15 per person 
 for a 45-minute session) and the chance to climb our exciting\, 50-foot T
 ango Tower ($25 per person for a one-hour session).\nS’mores kits will al
 so be available for roasting on-site for $5 per two-pack — the perfect wa
 y to top off your visit!\n\nHosted by: Bradford Woods\n\nAdditional Infor
 mation can be found at: https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/12433818
DTEND:20260509T180000Z
DTSTAMP:20260508T023829Z
DTSTART:20260509T140000Z
GEO:39.507470;-86.429030
LOCATION:Bradford Woods
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Bradford Woods Open Gate Day
UID:https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/12433818
URL:https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/12433818
X-HOSTS:Bradford Woods
END:VEVENT
